{"tid":1089651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑洞事件視界望遠鏡將有重大發表","createTime":"2019-04-03T02:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T04:36:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35acb6f9305357398524fbbd855e404610e7012d","tid":1089651,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eso.org/public/announcements/ann19018/?utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=SocialSignIn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eso.org%2Fpublic%2Fannouncements%2Fann19018%2F%3Futm_source%3DTwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3DSocialSignIn&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4a5172e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eso.org/public/announcements/ann19018/?utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=SocialSignIn</a><br />\n<br />\n歐洲南方天文台ESO即將在下禮拜三召開記者會 他們預告此次的觀測成果&quot;非常重要&quot;&quot;很有開創性&quot;  媒體猜測很可能是要公布人類史上首張黑洞照片<br />\n <br />\n事件視界望遠鏡（EHT）是以觀測大質量黑洞為目標的計畫。該計劃結合世界各地的電波望遠鏡，讓各天線互相協調、同時觀測同一目標並記錄下數據，形成一口徑等效於地球直徑的虛擬望遠鏡，將望遠鏡的角解析力提升至足以觀測事件視界的尺度。<br />\n <br />\nEHT的觀測目的<br />\n1.檢驗愛因斯坦廣義相對論<br />\n2.黑洞的吸積盤<br />\n3.黑洞噴流(超相對論性噴流)<br />\n4.事件視界存在與否<br />\n <br />\nEHT的兩大觀測對象:<br />\n1.南半天球 銀河系中央的超大質量黑洞人馬座 A*<br />\n2.北半天球 處女 A 星系中央的超大質量黑洞M87。<br />\n <br />\n我國中研院也有參與這項計畫  下禮拜三晚上九點會跟比利時、智利 ALMA 天文台、中國上海、日本、美國華盛頓特區同步召開記者會"},{"pid":"93cb30aca001adec2e10c5e05bba290aeba1358a","tid":1089651,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"等左張相好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於砌好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff82eb15f5cf2b3ca17af8e862404edf3ec2dbc1","tid":1089651,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"唔知似唔似interstellar個黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b43e7a8cad0a15c5f715be40c7ef470ff4326c","tid":1089651,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"雪山白鳳凰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc34e8e71f348046bd7b11ef9eee4d774751701e","tid":1089651,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"留名睇高清無碼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6197ea7f4505005b6ff9412ef3c540bb0d198d7b","tid":1089651,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"留名睇冇特別比連登仔屌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f089169df734c73b26d88b08202054bf5c7d5ce4","tid":1089651,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64870065329c2414892529989a35cd5b1091c0b","tid":1089651,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560717b649cc9ea456550ab7710acc1e90536883","tid":1089651,"uid":25514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"高清無碼黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62e8fa5c446f74f4c2eecd44d2f193211155372","tid":1089651,"uid":195714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wallpapercave.com/wp/DTvUQor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A